title: CleanMyMac v3.8.4 Final Patched [Mac OSX]
description: Mac cleaning software. Clean, optimize, and maintain your Mac with the all-new CleanMyMac 3. Plus, it knows exactly what can be safely cleaned from your Mac and what can’t. Almost like it’s got a brain or something.Macs are easy to use. Mac cleaners should be too. And, it only selects files that are 100% safe-to-delete, so you never have to worry about removing the wrong ones. It’s not just an automatic cleaning utility — it’s incredibly smart
